name: Clip-In Hair Extensions-12pcs/set Body Wave
description:
Our Clip on extension sets are convenient, far less expensive and give you the freedom to put them on whenever YOU want. Because Crown of Glory Hair Extensions are made from real human hair, you can dye it, style it and cut it – just like your own hair!

One set includes:
2 x 8inch 3 clips
4 x 6inch 3 clips
4 x 4inch 2 clips
2 x 1inch 1 clip

name: Denman Brush
description:
**We recommend using a 'Denman' brush to maintain your hair extensions**

The classic Denman brush continues to be an essential styling tool for professional hairdressers the world over.

Smooth, round-ended nylon pins in a staggered formation provide exceptional grip and control for maintaining tension on the hair while styling. The famous half-round rubber pad is perfect for smoothing hair, creating sleek bob shapes and for flicking out.

Incorporating the classic Denman ‘teardrop’ handles for comfortable salon styling. -Denman Inc.
